Other , as yet unnamed , cities will follow .
If all goes well , the product will be rolled out for national sales sometime next year , a Coke spokesman said .
After the confusion surrounding the change of the Coke formula in 1985 , Coca-Cola was reluctant to clutter the Classic name with a brand extension .
But now , the soft-drink giant appears willing to take the risk .
